nodes.text: Unidentified Resolute naval officer (Battle of Kamino)

This clone naval officer was stationed on the bridge of the Resolute and served under the command of Admiral Wullf Yularen around 21 BBY during the events of the Battle of Kamino. After the Separatists began their attack, this Clone naval officer informed Admiral Yularen that the Separatist fleet were pressing their attack and he was told to contact command at Tipoca City.
